    👋 Hey { $name }!
    I'm your music companion — search any track, get lyrics, remix it with FX,
    and discover similar songs.

    Tap an example below or just send me a song name 🎵
help =
    🎵 <b>How to use me</b>

    • Send any song/artist name to search
    • Tap a result to get the track
    • Use 🎛️ Remix for Nightcore, Slowed, 8D and more
    • Tap 🎤 Lyrics for lyrics + translation
    • Inline: type <code>@bot query</code> in any chat

